---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-amber-400 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-14">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between"
      >
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <p
            class="text-white/90 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm"
          >
            INFO YOU CAN TRUST
          </p>
          <h1
            class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight mt-2"
          >
            Certifications & Continued Education
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-white/95 text-base md:text-lg">
            This page is here for one reason: transparency. No gimmicks — just
            proof of standards, ethics, and ongoing development.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScjlcKsoJQrxMeoLpclzdXDWaa1ODLkN5mDord-UFvnTZ_CsA/viewform?usp=header&utm_source=website&utm_medium=certifications-hero&utm_campaign=apply&utm_id=certifications"
              target="_blank"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold uppercase hover:bg-black transition"
            >
              Book a Consult
            </a>
            <a
              href="#proof"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-yellow-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold uppercase hover:bg-yellow-50 transition"
            >
              View Proof
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust Stack -->
        <div
          class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl border border-white/20 p-6 md:w-[360px]"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-5 h-5"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 8 12 4.16-1.26 8-6.45 8-12V5l-8-3z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="font-bold uppercase">Training Standards</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-white/95 text-sm">
            <li>• Ethical communication-first approach</li>
            <li>• Real-world proofing (not sterile drills)</li>
            <li>• Clear owner coaching & homework systems</li>
            <li>• Tools used responsibly and transparently</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-white/80">
            If you ever have questions about a credential, ask — we’ll explain
            it in normal-people terms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-5 text-sm text-gray-500">
    <a
      href="https://leashlegacyk9.com/"
      class="hover:text-yellow-600 transition">Home</a
    >
    <span class="mx-2">/</span>
    <span class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">Certifications</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Certifications Grid -->
  <section class="py-14 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <p class="text-green-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
          What We’re Verified In
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
          Core Credentials
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card -->
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition bg-white p-6"
        >
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">AKC CGC Evaluator</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
                Manners, neutrality, and real-world obedience standards.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-bold uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border border-emerald-100"
            >
              Verified
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>• Preps dogs for CGC skills & public behavior</li>
            <li>• Helps owners build clean, test-ready handling</li>
            <li>• Focus on calm control around distractions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Card -->
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition bg-white p-6"
        >
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">
                Ethical E-Collar Conditioning
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
                Communication tool used responsibly — not punishment.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-bold uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-800 border border-yellow-100"
            >
              Standards
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>• Low-level intro paired with rewards</li>
            <li>• Clear timing, calm handling, no intimidation</li>
            <li>• Used for safety + reliability (especially off-leash)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Card -->
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition bg-white p-6"
        >
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">
                Handler Coaching Systems
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
                Owner skill-building so results stick at home.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-bold uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-sky-50 text-sky-700 border border-sky-100"
            >
              Practical
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>• Mechanics, timing, consistency, and structure</li>
            <li>• Real-world scenarios (not “perfect room” training)</li>
            <li>• Builds calm leadership without force</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Note -->
      <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <span class="font-bold">Real talk:</span> A certificate doesn’t train your
          dog — the system does. We use credentials as a baseline, then we prove it
          with results in your world: your neighborhood, your distractions, your life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof / Downloads -->
  <section id="proof" class="py-14 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <p class="text-green-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
          Transparency
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
          Proof & Documents
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Proof Card -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Certificate Scan (PDF)</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Download Here.</p>
          <a
            href="../certs/akc-cgc-evaluator.pdf"
            target="_blank"
            class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-gray-900 text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase hover:bg-black transition"
          >
            Download
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Verification Link</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            State: Virginia | City: Bassett | Jeremy Massey
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://www.apps.akc.org/cgc-evaluator/#"
            target="_blank"
            class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-yellow-500 text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase hover:bg-yellow-600 transition"
          >
            Verify Online
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Continued Education</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Courses, seminars, workshops, mentorships.
          </p>
          <a
            href="#education"
            class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full border border-gray-300 bg-white text-gray-900 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase hover:bg-gray-50 transition"
          >
            Jump to List
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Continued Education -->
  <section id="education" class="py-14 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <p class="text-green-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
          Always Learning
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
          Continued Education
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          This is where you list ongoing growth — updated methods, workshops,
          advanced behavior topics, etc.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Workshops / Seminars</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>• Reactivity And Behavioral Conference — (06/2025)</li>
            <li>• Handler and The Importance of Alpha — (09/2025)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Study Topics</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>• Reactivity & arousal regulation</li>
            <li>• Engagement + handler mechanics</li>
            <li>• Ethical tool conditioning & safety</li>
            <li>• Real-world proofing systems</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScjlcKsoJQrxMeoLpclzdXDWaa1ODLkN5mDord-UFvnTZ_CsA/viewform?usp=header&utm_source=website&utm_medium=certifications-cta&utm_campaign=apply&utm_id=certifications"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold uppercase hover:bg-green-700 transition"
        >
          Work With Leash Legacy
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
          Want a calmer dog fast? Let’s build the plan.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-14 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Certification FAQ</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
          Quick answers for people who just want the truth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details
          class="bg-white border border-yellow-400 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm"
        >
          <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer text-lg"
            >Do certifications guarantee results?</summary
          >
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
            No. They show baseline standards and education. Results come from a
            solid plan, reps, and consistency — and we coach that part hard.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details
          class="bg-white border border-yellow-400 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm"
        >
          <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer text-lg"
            >Do you train without an e-collar?</summary
          >
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
            Yes. Tools are optional and based on your goals, your dog, and your
            comfort level. We can do leash + reward-based systems only.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details
          class="bg-white border border-yellow-400 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm"
        >
          <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer text-lg"
            >Why show proof on a page?</summary
          >
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
            Because people deserve transparency. If you’re trusting someone with
            your dog, you should know what standards they follow.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
